<i>noun</i>: 흉 [흉], 욕질 [욕찔], 욕지거리 [욕찌거리], 욕설 [욕썰], 모욕 [모ː욕], 모독 [모ː독], 능욕 [능욕], 곤욕 [고ː뇩] <i>verb</i>: 모욕하다 [모ː요카다], 모독하다 [모ː도카다], 능욕하다 [능요카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흉 [흉]</dt><br>
<dd>1. scar</dd><br>
<dd>상처가 아물고 남은 자국.</dd><br>
<dd>The trace left after a wound has healed.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fault; insult</dd><br>
<dd>남에게 비웃음을 살 만한 말이나 행동.</dd><br>
<dd>Words or deeds that may be mocked by others.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>욕질 [욕찔]</dt><br>
<dd>curse; abuse; insult</dd><br>
<dd>욕하는 짓.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of using abusive language.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>욕지거리 [욕찌거리]</dt><br>
<dd>curse; abuse; insult</dd><br>
<dd>(속된 말로) 욕설.</dd><br>
<dd>(slang) Abusive and insulting words.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>욕설 [욕썰]</dt><br>
<dd>curse; abuse; insult</dd><br>
<dd>남을 무시하거나 비난하는 상스러운 말.</dd><br>
<dd>A vulgar remark which insults or blames another.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>모욕 [모ː욕]</dt><br>
<dd>insult; affront</dd><br>
<dd>낮추어 보고 창피를 주고 불명예스럽게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of defaming, humiliating, and looking down on someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>모독 [모ː독]</dt><br>
<dd>insult</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동으로 어떤 대상을 부끄럽고 수치스럽게 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of making someone feel humiliated and ashamed with words or actions.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>능욕 [능욕]</dt><br>
<dd>1. insult; humiliation</dd><br>
<dd>남을 하찮게 여겨 욕되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An insult at another person by belittling him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rape; assault</dd><br>
<dd>여자를 강간하여 욕되게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An insult at a female by raping her.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>곤욕 [고ː뇩]</dt><br>
<dd>trouble; insult</dd><br>
<dd>심한 모욕이나 참기 힘든 일.</dd><br>
<dd>A severe insult or a situation hard to endure.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>모욕하다 [모ː요카다]</dt><br>
<dd>insult</dd><br>
<dd>낮추어 보고 창피를 주고 불명예스럽게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To look down on, humiliate, and dishonor someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>모독하다 [모ː도카다]</dt><br>
<dd>insult</dd><br>
<dd>말이나 행동으로 어떤 대상을 부끄럽고 수치스럽게 만들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make someone feel humiliated and ashamed with words or actions.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>능욕하다 [능요카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. insult; humiliate</dd><br>
<dd>남을 하찮게 여겨 욕되게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To insult another person by belittling him/her.</dd><br>
<dd>2. rape; assault</dd><br>
<dd>여자를 강간하여 욕되게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To insult a female by raping her.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>